text: Have you or any family member/s have been diagnosed with or tested positive for COVID-19 in the past three (3) months?
Do you or did you have the following symptoms in the past 14 days:
Fever of greater than 37 degrees?
Do you have any flu-like symptom such as cough or chills in the past 14 days?
Do you experience shortness of breath or breathing difficulty?
Headache, muscle, or body ache?
Are you experiencing diarrhea?
Do you have any allergy to food, antibiotics, or any medicine?
Have you ever had a severe reaction to vaccines in the past?
Have you received any vaccine in the last 14 days?
For women:
Are you pregnant?
For women who are pregnant, are you in your 1st to 2nd trimester (1 to 6 months) of pregnancy?
Plans to get pregnant in the next 6 months?

Do you have a bleeding disorder or are you taking a blood thinner? (Example of Bleeding disorder: Hemophilia, Thalassemia) (Example of blood thinning medications: Aspirin, Clopidogrel, Warfarin, Cilostazol)
Do you have any of the following illness/disease?
Autoimmune disease
HIV Diagnosis
Cancer/Malignancy
Transplant Patient
Under steroid treatment
Bed ridden, terminal illness, less than 6mos prognosis
Are you bedridden?
Are you wheelchair bound?
